				\begin{document}$${\tau }_{{{{\rm{heartwood}}}}}={C}_{{{{\rm{heartwood}}}}}\cdot {f}_{{{{\rm{heartwood}}}}}\cdot (1+{{{\rm{HD}}}}+{{{\rm{FD}}}})$$\end{document}τheartwood=Cheartwood⋅fheartwood⋅(1+HD+FD)14\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
