				\begin{document}$${\tau }_{{{{\rm{leaf}}}}}=\left\{\begin{array}{ll}{C}_{{{{\rm{leaf}}}}}\cdot \frac{1}{{a}_{{{{\rm{ll}}}}}}&{{{\rm{evergreen}}}}\\ {C}_{{{{\rm{leaf}}}}}\cdot 1&{{{\rm{deciduous}}}}\\ \end{array}\right.$$\end{document}τleaf=Cleaf⋅1allevergreenCleaf⋅1deciduousFurther, for leaf longevities longer than a year, the carbon costs of fineroot and leaf turnover are assumed to be proportional28:16\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
