				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\tau }_{{{{\rm{fineroot}}}}}=\left\{\begin{array}{ll}{C}_{{{{\rm{fineroot}}}}}\cdot \frac{1}{{a}_{{{{\rm{ll}}}}}}&{a}_{{{{\rm{ll}}}}} > 1\\ {C}_{{{{\rm{fineroot}}}}}\cdot 1&{a}_{{{{\rm{ll}}}}}\le 1\\ \end{array}\right.$$\end{document}τfineroot=Cfineroot⋅1allall>1Cfineroot⋅1all≤1Subsequently, the annual carbon balance can be calculated as:17\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
