				\begin{document}$${T}_{{{{\rm{mean,plant,new}}}}}={T}_{{{{\rm{mean,plant,old}}}}}+{{{\mathcal{N}}}}(\alpha,0.05)\cdot ({T}_{{{{\rm{mean,local}}}}}-{T}_{{{{\rm{mean,plant,old}}}}})$$\end{document}Tmean,plant,new=Tmean,plant,old+N(α,0.05)⋅(Tmean,local−Tmean,plant,old)Where “target" denotes the trait value predicted to be optimal from the optimisation procedure, and “local" is the local climatic variable. To allow a limited degree stochasticity in the evolutionary adaptation in space and time \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
